OL,3,CFamine rises in war-torn Sudan with
OL,4,C750,000 at risk of dying from
OL,5,Cstarvation
OL,7,FSudan descended into conflict in April
OL,8,F2023. Since then, millions have been
OL,9,Fdisplaced, food supplies are cramped
OL,10,Fand 14,000 people have been killed,
OL,11,FITV News Correspondent Lucy Watson
OL,12,Freports
OL,14,FHundreds of thousands of people are
OL,15,Fnow at imminent risk of starvation in
OL,16,FSudan, as the catastrophic
OL,17,Fhumanitarian crisis in the country
OL,18,Fcontinues to intensify after more than
OL,19,Fa year of violent conflict.
