OL,3,CFamine rises in war-torn Sudan with
OL,4,C750,000 at risk of dying from
OL,5,Cstarvation
OL,7,FThis is according to a new report
OL,8,Freleased on Thursday by the IPC
OL,9,F(Integrated Food Security Phase
OL,10,FClassification) - a United Nations
OL,11,F(UN)-backed initiative that monitors
OL,12,Fthe severity and magnitude of hunger
OL,13,Fcrises.
OL,15,FThe report shows that looking from
OL,16,FJune to September, the number of
OL,17,Fpeople in catastrophic hunger (the
OL,18,Fmost severe level) is expected to rise
OL,19,Ffrom 109,000 to 755,000 people.
