OL,3,CFamine rises in war-torn Sudan with
OL,4,C750,000 at risk of dying from
OL,5,Cstarvation
OL,7,FThe conflict created the world's
OL,8,Flargest displacement crisis with more
OL,9,Fthan 10 million people forced to flee
OL,10,Ftheir homes, the International
OL,11,FOrganization for Migration (IOM) said
OL,12,Fin June.
OL,14,FHuman rights experts working for the
OL,15,FUN said that both warring sides used
OL,16,Ffood and starvation as a war weapon.
