OL,3,CFamine rises in war-torn Sudan with
OL,4,C750,000 at risk of dying from
OL,5,Cstarvation
OL,7,FAnother 8.5 million people are
OL,8,Fclassified in the second worst level
OL,9,Fof starvation, or Phase 4, meaning
OL,10,Fthat the risk of hunger-related death
OL,11,Fis rapidly increasing, the IPC report
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThose people are facing extreme food
OL,15,Fshortages, acute malnutrition and
OL,16,Fexcessively high disease levels, it
OL,17,Fadded.
