OL,3,CFamine rises in war-torn Sudan with
OL,4,C750,000 at risk of dying from
OL,5,Cstarvation
OL,7,F'This is a crisis that desperately
OL,8,Fneeds the worlds attention,' David
OL,9,FMiliband, President and CEO of the
OL,10,FInternational Rescue Committee told
OL,11,FITV News
OL,13,F"The conflict has not only triggered
OL,14,Fmass displacement and disruption of
OL,15,Fsupply routes, market systems and
OL,16,Fagricultural production, it has also
OL,17,Fseverely limited access to essential
OL,18,Fhumanitarian assistance, exacerbating
OL,19,Fan already dire situation," the report
OL,20,Fsaid.
