OL,3,CFamine rises in war-torn Sudan with
OL,4,C750,000 at risk of dying from
OL,5,Cstarvation
OL,7,FAt particular risk are children,
OL,8,Fpregnant and breastfeeding women, and
OL,9,Fthe elderly. About 4 million children
OL,10,Funder 5 suffer from acute
OL,11,Fmalnutrition, with 730,000 of those
OL,12,Fprojected to be at imminent risk of
OL,13,Fdying, said UNICEF Executive Director
OL,14,FCatherine Russell.
