OL,3,CFamine rises in war-torn Sudan with
OL,4,C750,000 at risk of dying from
OL,5,Cstarvation
OL,7,F"The consequences of the violence, of
OL,8,Fthe displacement of the, you know,
OL,9,Flack of food, the lack of security is
OL,10,Fjust devastating for women and
OL,11,Fchildren in Sudan," Ms Russell said in
OL,12,Fan interview after her trip to Sudan
OL,13,Fearlier this week.
OL,15,F"It's important for the international
OL,16,Fcommunity to realise that we have to
OL,17,Fget more resources to Sudan," she said.
OL,19,F"But we also need to push the parties,
OL,20,Fhopefully, to peace. That's really, at
OL,21,Fthe end of the day. what we need here."
